  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (ad751b2 2023-05-28T00:04:05.718310776Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nanvil\n\n### Operating System\n\nLinux\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nThe `baseFeePerGas` decreases even when the block is full. To reproduce, run `anvil -b 1`  (set a block time to make it easy to track block headers) and send transactions the use the gas limit.",
